videos.description: Utah's Sedrick Barefield delivers an assist to David Collette while having three defenders covering him.
videos.headline: Ridiculous pass sets up Utah layup

videos.description: Utah's Lorenzo Bonam finds an open David Collette open down court where he's fouled after making a layup.
videos.headline: Great outlet pass leads to and-1 for Utah

videos.description: Oregon State's Stephen Thompson Jr. makes a wide-open 3-pointer to cut the Utah lead to 64-63.
videos.headline: Oregon State pulls within one late in the game

videos.description: Utah's Kyle Kuzma knocks down a 3-pointer and Oregon State's Stephen Thompson Jr. answers with a quick layup.
videos.headline: Both teams trade buckets in the final minute to keep the game close

videos.description: Oregon State's Stephen Thompson Jr. makes a layup to give Oregon State a 68-67 lead over Utah with ten seconds remaining in the game.
videos.headline: Thompson Jr. gives Oregon State the lead with ten seconds left

videos.description: Oregon State's Stephen Thompson Jr. discusses his thoughts on his team's performance in their 68-67 comeback win over Utah.
videos.headline: Stephen Thompson Jr. talks about 68-67 comeback victory over Utah
